::Amperion::
       He continues to ignore Empath and looks over at Sanguine.  "I've got 
Amperion, lallseday."  He continues repeating the phrase until the pain from 
Empath's hit registers in his head.  The pain causes him to wince and then 
continue to repeat "I've got Amperion, lallseday."
